# Git Workflow

- Branch: `feat/`, `fix/`, `chore/`, `docs/` + short description
- Commits: [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/) — `feat:`, `fix:`, `test:`, `docs:`
- One logical change per commit; PR groups related commits
- **Never** push directly to `main` — PR + review + CI green
- **Never** force push to `main`/`master`
- **Never** commit: `.env`, secrets, `node_modules/`, build artifacts
- Do not amend pushed commits unless explicitly requested

PR template: `projects/fieldforge/.github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md`
